    "title": "Opening for Store Manager at Starbucks India International Enterprises",
    "description": "Grow your career with Starbucks India International Enterprises! We are hiring a Store Manager for our Vadodara team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Starbucks India International Enterprises:\nStarbucks India International Enterprises is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Maintain high standards of store hygiene and cleanliness\n• Train and motivate the sales team to deliver excellent service\n• Prepare daily sales reports and share insights with management\n• Assist in recruiting, onboarding, and performance management of staff\n• Ensure compliance with company policies and retail regulations\n• Manage store operations to ensure smooth daily functioning\n• Monitor inventory levels and coordinate replenishment activities\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Retail Analytics\n• Proficiency in Visual Merchandising\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Sales Techniques\n• Proficiency in KPI Management\n• Proficiency in CRM\n• Proficiency in Team Leadership\n• Proficiency in E-commerce Integration\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Flexible working hours\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Vadodara, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Starbucks India International Enterprises!",
